OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780683078
OL,3,CAmbulance worker further arrested
OL,4,Cafter six deaths in healthcare settings
OL,6,FPolice investigating the deaths of six
OL,7,Fpeople in a health care setting in
OL,8,FWiltshire have further arrested a 35-
OL,9,Fyear-old ambulance worker.
OL,11,FThe man, from West Wiltshire, had
OL,12,Fpreviously been arrested on suspicion
OL,13,Fof six counts of gross negligence
OL,14,Fmanslaughter and four counts of ill-
OL,15,Ftreatment or wilful neglect by a care
OL,16,Fworker.
OL,18,FNow, he has been further arrested on
OL,19,Fanother two counts of wilful neglect
OL,20,Fby a care worker.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
