CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780683078
OL,3,CAmbulance worker further arrested
OL,4,Cafter six deaths in healthcare settings
OL,6,FHe has remained on bail since
OL,7,FSeptember 2025.
OL,9,FA second ambulance worker, a 60-year-
OL,10,Fold woman, who was arrested on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of gross negligence
OL,12,Fmanslaughter and wilful neglect also
OL,13,Fremains on bail.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
