PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780683078
OL,3,CAmbulance worker further arrested
OL,4,Cafter six deaths in healthcare settings
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the South Western
OL,7,FAmbulance Service NHS Foundation
OL,8,FTrust, said: "As soon as the Trust
OL,9,Fbecame aware of any concerns, we
OL,10,Fimmediately launched an internal
OL,11,Finvestigation which resulted in a
OL,12,Fprompt police referral, and we
OL,13,Fcontinue to work closely with
OL,14,FWiltshire Police as part of their
OL,15,Fongoing investigation.
OL,26,@pD@NOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
