FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780683078
OL,3,CAmbulance worker further arrested
OL,4,Cafter six deaths in healthcare settings
OL,6,F"Two members of staff have been
OL,7,Fdismissed from the Trust, following an
OL,8,Finitial suspension. This meant that
OL,9,Fthey were immediately relieved of all
OL,10,Fduties, including the treatment of
OL,11,Fpatients.
OL,13,F"We would like to reassure communities
OL,14,Fthat there is no on-going risk to
OL,15,Fpatients. Please continue to call 999
OL,16,Fin a life-threatening emergency.
OL,18,F"Due to the ongoing investigation,
OL,19,Fthere will be no further comment at
OL,20,Fthis stage."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
