CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780683078
OL,3,CAmbulance worker further arrested
OL,4,Cafter six deaths in healthcare settings
OL,6,FThe investigation, known as Operation
OL,7,FWillow, has been ongoing following
OL,8,Fconcerns raised to Wiltshire Police in
OL,9,F2023.
OL,11,FThe force is asking anyone with
OL,12,Finformation to contact them online.
